 Billy Bostock 
Billy Bostock was one of those people you rarely meet more than once. He had a unique energy and humor that made him very popular. He was a very passionate person, if you crossed him or his friends he was quick to throw fists. Billy was a great to friend in any situation having fun or in a fight. He will be Memorials remembered.

Billy Bostock died May 30th, 1997 in Fresno California when the car he was in was hit from the side and rolled upside down into a waterfilled ditch. His pregnant girlfriend and her father also died in the accident. He was about to graduate from high school, a goal his youth might not have allowed.
